{"tid":303021,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唔放屁唔撩鼻屎！楊冪自爆大髀開刀抽脂","createTime":"2017-06-29T23:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T06:48:21.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6603f52e2f224fbadcc59783e342107f44b6e7c","tid":303021,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170629181218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170629181218&h=63b74f2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊冪話自己唔放屁唔撩鼻屎，果然係靚女呀！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170629181218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170629181218&h=3ba9e606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊冪揸住棵西蘭花出場，佢話自己沒有鼻屎！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170629181218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170629181218&h=ba8c8321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦都唔放屁～<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_04b.jpg?20170629181218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20170629181218&h=8b94b456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽到小S都呆咗問佢係咪人嚟？<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_05b.jpg?20170629181218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20170629181218&h=0ab1d171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊冪喺節目上繼續自嘲，話自己其實好多肉！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_06b.jpg?20170629181218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20170629181218&h=52af7859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小S摸完嘅反應，好似誇張咗啲呀？<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_07b.jpg?20170629181218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20170629181218&h=d38a1d7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解咁白？因為搽咗咁厚嘅粉底！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_08b.jpg?20170629181218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20170629181218&h=309f16b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊冪出名腳長，小S忍唔唔住問：「有沒有打陰影？」<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_09b.jpg?20170629181218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_09b.jpg%3F20170629181218&h=b1ba7390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一山還有一山高，楊冪再「自爆」大髀開刀抽脂，問你死未？<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_10b.jpg?20170629181218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_10b.jpg%3F20170629181218&h=4719ba07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當「女神」遇上女神時&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/photo/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_11b.jpg?20170629181218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001_11b.jpg%3F20170629181218&h=c63cdf20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林心如（資料圖片）<br />\n台灣女星小S（徐熙娣）主持嘅綜藝節目《姐姐好餓2》最新一集邀請咗楊冪做嘉賓，而喺節目預告中，楊冪多次自嘲，搞到小S都差啲招架唔住，不過遇強愈強，兩人仲愈講愈多，楊冪仲話自己唔會放屁𠻹！<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，靚女係唔會屙屎、唔會放屁嘅！睇嚟楊冪都知自己係靚女嚟，好有自信咁話自己唔會撩鼻屎，唔會放屁，搞到小S都就嚟反白眼問佢：「你是人嗎？」不過，其實佢哋都係講笑啫！<br />\n<br />\n楊冪唔只講自己，連好姊妹林心如都「出賣」，踢爆林心如減肥內幕，再補多刀話：「看她好像也沒有甚麼效果！」小S聽到都忍唔住話：「Oh My God，原來你是笑裏藏刀的人！」<br />\n<br />\n跟住楊冪繼續自嘲又自揭缺點，身材高挑嘅佢話自己手臂其實有好多肉，呢個時候小S走去摸，一摸完誇張Mode話：「怎樣那麼囊？」小S都出名轉數快問題又夠直接，當佢望住楊冪條長腿時就問：「有沒有打陰影？」點知一山還有一山高，楊冪再發功，「自爆」大髀開刀抽脂又話塊面咁白係化咗好厚粉底，自嘲功力同佢啲粉底一樣「非常深厚」，睇嚟「女神」小S遇上呢位女神，應該「鬥餐死」喇！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001.html?refer=fn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170629%2Fbkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001.html%3Frefer%3Dfn2&d=Lef6mzCXcJ9AA5ymDh00qMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=3aa11b34\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170629/bkn-20170629114352753-0629_00862_001.html?refer=fn2</a>"},{"pid":"fde221a92ca96b84d09eb3097825a18ba991bbdc","tid":303021,"uid":16528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:52:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">等姨殺</span></span>"},{"pid":"d75194d2ec9c3d788efd009b476452cdf2a0fe34","tid":303021,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:54:57.000Z","msg":"以前好靚 乜而家個樣咁假ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c744e6e959be4753c75bf7a18984031b997c9c","t